there's a deeper need,

50:45.867 --> 50:47.567
a deeper hunger,

50:47.633 --> 50:52.200
an emptiness
that has to be filled.

50:52.266 --> 50:53.867
So Tobias,

50:53.934 --> 50:57.300
why don't you tell us
what you're addicted to?

50:58.333 --> 51:01.934
- You know.
They know.

51:02.000 --> 51:03.400
- Yeah, okay.

51:03.467 --> 51:06.667
Augustus, you want to talk
about your addiction?

51:06.734 --> 51:08.800
- I was a crack addict.

51:08.867 --> 51:10.934
I've been squeaky clean
for 22 months.

51:11.000 --> 51:13.133
- Yes! Ron?
[heartbeat pounding]

51:13.200 --> 51:17.066
- Speed's my fave.
- How long you been clean?

51:17.133 --> 51:19.467
- A year.

51:19.533 --> 51:21.700
- Whitney.

51:21.767 --> 51:25.066
- I quit seven times over
the last 52 years,

51:25.133 --> 51:26.834
this being
my longest period,

51:26.900 --> 51:30.467
five years, three months
and six days.

51:30.533 --> 51:32.033
- What are you addicted to?

51:32.100 --> 51:33.800
- What, since I've been inside?
- Yeah.

51:33.867 --> 51:36.200
- Anything I can
get my hands on.

51:36.266 --> 51:37.934
But originally opium.

51:38.000 --> 51:40.934
[jazzy music]

51:41.000 --> 51:46.734
♪ ♪

51:46.800 --> 51:51.066
I had been decorated with
the Purple Heart for valor.

51:51.133 --> 51:53.567
[chuckles]
Valor.

51:53.633 --> 51:57.567
Only I knew I was
really a fraud.

51:57.633 --> 51:59.100
Even after
I was discharged,

51:59.166 --> 52:01.834
I couldn't take
the uniform off.

52:01.900 --> 52:04.633
During the war,
while I was in the Orient,

52:04.700 --> 52:07.066
I got hooked into opium.

52:07.133 --> 52:11.066
My true self lay in
that Quixotic little drug.

52:11.133 --> 52:15.867
♪ ♪

52:15.934 --> 52:19.066
- [moaning]

52:19.133 --> 52:22.834
[groaning]

52:22.900 --> 52:27.467
- Prisoner number 45M242,
Whitney Munson.

52:27.533 --> 52:30.133
Convicted march 7th, '45.

52:30.200 --> 52:31.667
Murder in
the first degree,

52:31.734 --> 52:33.834
criminal possession
of a controlled substance.

52:33.900 --> 52:36.800
Sentence: 110 years.

52:36.867 --> 52:39.667
Up for a parole in sixty.

52:39.734 --> 52:40.767
Question.

52:40.834 --> 52:42.333
Why'd you strangle
the whore?

52:42.400 --> 52:43.567
- I didn't think I was.

52:43.633 --> 52:46.333
I thought I was
being affectionate.

52:46.400 --> 52:50.233
Her neck was so pale.

52:50.300 --> 52:53.133
So thin, so fine.

52:53.200 --> 52:56.600
- And you've been in prison
for 52 years, right?

52:56.667 --> 52:58.000
- That's right.

52:58.066 --> 53:01.233
I've only got eight years
left until my parole.

53:01.300 --> 53:04.800
Come the year 2005,
I'm out of here.

53:04.867 --> 53:06.567
- Look, I can't stay
here anymore

53:06.633 --> 53:08.333
and listen to any more of
these fucking stories, okay?

53:08.400 --> 53:09.600
- Tobias, sit down.

53:09.667 --> 53:12.467
- No, it's not helping.
It's not helping!

53:12.533 --> 53:14.567
- Hey, hold it!

53:27.600 --> 53:29.166
- Hello.

53:29.233 --> 53:31.433
- Yeah, hiya.

53:31.500 --> 53:35.000
- I'm here to give
you a makeover.

53:35.066 --> 53:36.467
- Huh?

53:36.533 --> 53:38.900
- Your boyfriend
told me to.

53:40.967 --> 53:44.633
He said, don't take no
for an answer.

54:07.934 --> 54:10.900
- My God.

54:10.967 --> 54:13.066
You're even prettier
than I thought you'd be.

54:13.133 --> 54:15.433
[laughter]

54:27.834 --> 54:30.800
[tense music]

54:30.867 --> 54:34.066
♪ ♪

54:34.133 --> 54:36.967
- He really is
a beautiful baby.

54:37.033 --> 54:39.066
[speaking Spanish]

54:48.433 --> 54:50.767
- Miguel...

54:50.834 --> 54:52.266
your baby's dead.

54:55.166 --> 54:56.734
- Ah!

54:56.800 --> 54:59.000
[speaking Spanish]

55:07.934 --> 55:09.567
- I ain't saying
drugs are good,

55:09.633 --> 55:11.400
but when your past
has passed

55:11.467 --> 55:13.233
and your present sucks,

55:13.300 --> 55:15.800
your future holds
nothing but broken promises

55:15.867 --> 55:17.834
and dead dreams,

55:17.900 --> 55:19.533
the drugs,
they kill the pain.

55:19.600 --> 55:20.934
Listen up, America.

55:21.000 --> 55:23.467
You ain't never gonna
get rid of drugs

55:23.533 --> 55:26.934
until you cure pain.

55:46.100 --> 55:49.200
[tense jazzy music]

55:49.266 --> 55:56.300
♪ ♪

56:42.767 --> 56:44.834
[bright tone]
